      "cooked": "<p>Ahahaa. M’kujtove ate barcaleten Tirondon, me ate burrin qe kishte gruan shume te eger dhe duke dale kjo nga shtepia ai e pyet:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>ku po shkon?</li>\n<li>ca te duhet ty, ia kthen ajo.</li>\n<li>sa do vonohesh?</li>\n<li>sa t’me doje trapi.</li>\n<li>mire, vonohu sa te doje trapi, por asnje minut me shume degjove? - kercenon burri. <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/joy.png?v=5\" title=\":joy:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":joy:\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/joy.png?v=5\" title=\":joy:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":joy:\">\n</li>\n</ul>",
